high_descs: walk straight to the side of the table
Grab the cup from the coffee machine
Turn left, walk to the microwave
Put the cup in the microwave, close the microwave, heat the microwave, open the microwave, take the cup out, close the microwave
Turn around, walk back to the side of the white table
Put the cup under the coffee machine on the table
anns.task_desc: Heat the cup with microwave, put it back in the coffee machine

high_descs: Walk forward then turn left to face the table.
Pick up the coffee cup from the coffee maker.
Turn left and walk toward the microwave.
Open the microwave, place the cup inside, close the door and turn it on. Remove the cup when done and close the door.
Turn around and walk back to the table on the left.
Put the cup back in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved coffee cup in the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn to face the spatula on the white table.
Pick the mug up from the table.
Turn around and stand in front of the microwave.
Put the cup in the microwave, turn it on, take the cup back out and shut the door.
Turn around and go back to the white table that is behind.
Put the mug under the coffee maker on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a warmed cup on a table.
